  <brief_title>Effect of Intravenous Magnesium on Postoperative Sore Throat After Thyroidectomy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Ajou University School of Medicine</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Ajou University School of Medicine</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of intravenous magnesium on
      postoperative throat pain after thyroidectomy.

      The secondary purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of intravenous magnesium on
      total dose of fentanyl in recovery room after thyroidectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
